For UE5 material work, follow agent-pack/SPEC.md and only use node types from agent-pack/nodes-ue5.7.json (plus the reserved types MaterialOutput/FunctionInput/FunctionOutput/MaterialFunctionCall). Write each material to its own project folder: `graphs/<project>/<material_name>.matgraph.json` plus any MaterialFunctions it uses as siblings in the same folder. Connections use "node:pin" strings. Never write x/y positions.
